OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSpells of
OL,6,Flate sunshine in the east but cloud
OL,7,Fspreading in from the west with a few
OL,8,Fspots of light rain, though many
OL,9,Fremaining dry. Low cloud and coastal
OL,10,Ffog arriving in the west overnight. A
OL,11,Fmild night for many.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FLow cloud retreating back to
OL,14,Fwestern coasts, where it may locally
OL,15,Fpersist. A dry, bright and warm day
OL,16,Ffor most inland, although sunshine may
OL,17,Fbe slightly hazy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
